Titolo: Gears Tactics

Anno: 2020

Descrizione: Gears Tactics is a turn-based tactics video game developed by Splash Damage in conjunction with The Coalition and published by Xbox Game Studios. It is a spin-off of the Gears of War franchise and a prequel to the first game. The game was released first for Microsoft Windows on April 28, 2020 and subsequently for Xbox One and Xbox Series X/S on November 10, 2020.



Genere: Turn-based tactics

Valutazione: 81
